"35:43:4" : {s: 35, a: 43, w: 4, r: "مكر", t: "وَمَكْرَ", l: "مَكْر", lc: 19, tl: "wamakra", lb: "ষড়যন্ত্র, চক্রান্ত, কুট-কৌশল",e: "and plotting", b: "চক্রান্ত", f: 1, rm: "To practice deceit or guile or circumvention, practice evasion or elusion, to plot, to excercise art or craft or cunning, act with policy, practice strategem."},
