"35:44:19" : {s: 35, a: 44, w: 19, r: "عجز", t: "لِيُعْجِزَهُۥ", l: "يُعْجِزَ", lc: 4, tl: "liyuʿ'jizahu", lb: "অক্ষম করা",e: "that can escape (from) Him", b: "তাকে অক্ষম করে দেয়ার জন্য", f: 1, rm: "to become behind, lack, become in the rear, lag behind (strength), become incapable, powerless, be weak. ujuzun - old women. ajaza (vb. 4) to weaken, frustrate, find one to be weak. muajiz - one who baffles. ajzun (pl. ajazun) - portion of the trunk that is below its upper part."},
"35:44:20" : {s: 35, a: 44, w: 20, r: "", t: "مِن", l: "مِن", lc: 3067, tl: "min", lb: "মধ্য থেকে, কিছুর চেয়ে",e: "any", b: "থেকে, মধ্যে, ব্যতীত ", f: 859, rm: ""},
